info.author: Andrew Kovalev
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
This is Python wrapper for GDS Indexing API. Provides an easy access
through Python.
You can view how it works in our example file – example.py.
This library works fine with GDS 1.0 version.
info.keywords: GDS, Google Desktop Search, Add to GDS,GDS Python library, Python GDS
